(22450, 36071, 0, 1, 'Wait For A While (Live)', '是由作者本身生活情形發想......\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n身邊一個一個漂亮的女生\r\n\r\n卻往往不知道該如何出手\r\n\r\n對於朋友不斷的相拱\r\n\r\n只會用 " 再等等 再等等 "  來搪塞 \r\n\r\n顆顆\r\n\r\n', '2010-02-21 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 7, '“ What should I do to make you want me? ”\r\n(該怎麼做 才能讓你愛上我呢?)\r\n\r\nI really need to know the answer !\r\n(我真的急需知道答案呀)\r\n\r\nEven though you don’t know me now…\r\n(即使我們到現在還不認識)\r\n\r\nIt doesn’t matter ,\r\nIt doesn’t matter !!!\r\n(但我想 沒甚麼關係的 是吧!!)\r\n\r\nThe only thing I can do…\r\n(現在我唯一能做的)\r\n\r\nis just wait for a while\r\n(也只有慢慢的等了)\r\n\r\n\r\nThe day has finally come !\r\n(哇嗚 我們見面的這天終於要來了)\r\n\r\nI’m excited but also afraid (of it)\r\n(興奮跟害怕的心情同時充斥著我的心)\r\n\r\nI’m wondering what I have to say…\r\n(我還在想 等等我得說些甚麼才好呢!?)\r\n\r\nBut nothing ! Totally nothing in my mind !\r\n(唉唉 可是我的腦子卻是一片空白阿阿 )\r\n\r\nThe only thing I can do…\r\n\r\nis just wait for a while\r\n\r\n\r\nI don’t think I can wait all my life\r\n(我可不認為我可以一輩子這樣等下去)\r\n\r\nIt’s just like I am wasting my time\r\n(就好像不斷的不斷的浪費我的時間)\r\n\r\nGirl , if you can really hear me\r\n(女孩兒 要是你真的聽到我內心的呼喚)\r\n\r\nHelp me out! Help me out!!\r\n(救我吧 讓我脫離這個迴圈)\r\n\r\n\r\nLove , is just like magic\r\n(愛情就好像魔術一般阿)\r\n\r\nYou would never know what’s within..\r\n(他葫蘆裡賣甚麼藥我們永遠都不知道)\r\n\r\nDa la la la la la la\r\nLa la la la la la la\r\n\r\nThe only thing I can do…\r\n\r\nis just wait for a while\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nSorry , my girl , I didn’t mean to fuck up !\r\n(抱歉阿 親愛的 我不是故意讓一切變得這麼複雜的)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nbaby I don''t know why I am behind your sight\r\n(喔 女孩 我不懂為什麼我總是不在你的視線裡)\r\n\r\n\r\nYou know i really want you to stay by my side\r\n(我真的很希望你可以一直在我的身邊)\r\n\r\n\r\nit''s been so hard for me to make up my mind\r\n (但要下定決心真的好難阿QQ)\r\n.....................................................................................', '', 236, '', '棠棠', '棠棠', '星光盃熱門音樂大賽主辦單位', '', '', 0, 0, 1, '2010-02-21 15:55:01', '2013-10-07 17:15:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
